In device spec:

// specific x,y position
(gui: ( \x: 30, \y: 30, \width: 100, \height: 200))
(gui: ( \x: 30, \y: 30 ) // use default widths and height

// specify location by grid location (rows, columns)
(gui: ( \row: 1, \column: 2, \width: 100, \height: 200))
(gui: ( \row: 1, \column: 2) ); // use default widths and height
